This README file contains information on the contents of the meta-gcp-iot layer.

Please see the corresponding sections below for details.

Dependencies
============

This layer depends on:

    URI: git://github.com/mendersoftware/meta-mender/meta-mender-core
    branch: master
    revision: HEAD

in addition to any additional platform dependencies.  Specifically for
Raspberry Pi 3 builds you will need:

    URI: git://git.yoctoproject.org/meta-raspberrypi
    branch: master
    revision: HEAD

    URI: git://github.com/mendersoftware/meta-mender/meta-mender-raspberrypi
    branch: master
    revision: HEAD

Other platforms will vary.

Patches
=======

Please submit any patches against the meta-gcp-iot layer to the github repository:

Table of Contents
=================

  I. Adding the meta-gcp-iot layer to your build
 II. Misc


I. Adding the meta-gcp-iot layer to your build
=================================================

Run 'bitbake-layers add-layer meta-gcp-iot'

II. Misc
========

This layer contains additions for integrating your Yocto build with the Google Cloud Platform.